backup:  Create backup of 'git diff' + untracked files for all repositories specified in allRepoConfig with respect to both the last commit in local repo and remote repo.
backup --refRemote:  Create backup of 'git diff' + untracked files for all repositories specified in allRepoConfig with respect to the last commit in remote repo.
backup --refLocal:  Create backup of 'git diff' + untracked files for all repositories specified in allRepoConfig with respect to the last commit in local repo.